{"id":10000002,"title":"宝塔redis外网访问","introduction":"宝塔redis外网访问","cover":"https://joyimg.lexujia.com/blog/article-cover/20250416/17_IMG_202501164130_427x476.jpg","classifyId":100001,"columnId":null,"userId":10009,"content":"<p>修改Redis配置文件<br />\nRedis的配置文件通常位于/etc/redis/6379.conf（端口号可能不同，根据你的配置而定）。</p>\n<p>修改bind指令：默认情况下，Redis只监听本地地址。你需要将bind指令从127.0.0.1改为0.0.0.0，允许所有IP连接。</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-\">bind 0.0.0.0\n</code></pre>\n<p>修改protected-mode</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-\">protected-mode no\n</code></pre>\n<p>最后修改防火墙并重启</p>\n","readType":1,"isStick":2,"state":1,"isOriginal":2,"reprintAddress":null,"isRecommend":2,"readership":0,"keywords":"redis","userSource":2,"createTime":"2025-04-16 12:05:13","updateTime":"2026-04-16 15:43:11","likeCount":0,"classifyName":"运维部署","labels":[100005,100006],"labelNames":["宝塔","运维"],"userName":"徐徐乐之","userAvatar":"http://localhost:8000/article/08eee589-49e0-437c-987wdq.png","columnName":null}